data.description: Discover the allure of country living with this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style home nestled on 6.61 wooded acres. Nature lovers will delight in the Pier Cove Ravine meandering through the property. Inside, a cozy stone fireplace adds warmth to the inviting living space. The lower level holds potential with an unfinished 5th bedroom featuring egress window and a 3rd rough-plumbed bathroom. Embrace the rustic setting just 2 hours from Chicago and close to the shores of Lake Michigan. Your private escape awaits!
